<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/fd039245d688d43f12c98fef721ed21b0ef43b4e.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
中国折扇文化起源于宋代吗？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=4cc6a4b85ba205ce08f96064&lemmaId=3373422&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
清末和民国时，折扇是由两片大骨和若干小骨组成的，扇骨的数目称档，天津地区称之“根材”。譬如大骨二、小骨十四，皆称之为“十六档”或“十六根材”。清末民国时，最常见的是“九五十六根材”的扇骨，所谓“九五”是指扇骨长9寸5分。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-09-25</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">36</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="f78312c8893bb4e8f8fbf9ad">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=f78312c8893bb4e8f8fbf9ad&lemmaId=3373422&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/faf2b2119313b07ee1604b3001d7912397dd8c2c.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
折扇在明代是奢侈品？《金瓶梅》里西门庆给出答案
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=f78312c8893bb4e8f8fbf9ad&lemmaId=3373422&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
折扇约于十一世纪从日本经高丽传入中国，宋元间使用折扇的人还不多（戏剧《长生殿》里唐明皇和杨贵妃手持折扇属于“戏说”），至明代广泛流行，制扇作坊、扇铺遍布各地，有商人专以贩扇为业。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-08-20</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">51</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="3bad0e02c5f26a4dcbee9038">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=67db0100&authorId=b9ad24c52f69f5c5d50e5820&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/faf2b2119313b07ed2eb213e06d7912397dd8cb5.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>春梅狐狸</strong>
<span>“传统服饰”科普作者</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=3bad0e02c5f26a4dcbee9038&lemmaId=3373422&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/908fa0ec08fa513d1d6cb56a376d55fbb3fbd944.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
从外销扇到景区纪念品，鬼知道几百年里我们的审美经历了什么！
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=3bad0e02c5f26a4dcbee9038&lemmaId=3373422&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
我常常会困惑，折扇只是平常之物，我们花了无穷的气力去争论它是中国还是日本发明的，为何却拿不出一点点心思去了解折扇后来的故事，以致于我心头总难免一股“事已至此”的茫然。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-06-24</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">96</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
